casebody.data:
No. 394,

Misc.

Leight v. Schechter, Personnel Director and Chairman, Municipal Civil Service Commission, et al. Appellant-petitioner pro se. Peter Campbell Brown and Seymour B. Quel for appellees-respondents. Per Curiam:

The motion to dismiss is granted and the appeal is dismissed for want of a substantial. federal question. The petition for writ of certiorari is denied.
